documentation:
Materialize the run results for nodes. It walks through all runs and get the last results for primary run types.

The result format
{
   'node_id': {
      'row_count_diff': {
        'run_id': '<run_id>',
        'result': '<result>'
      },
      'value_diff': {
        'run_id': '<run_id>',
        'result': '<result>'
      },
   },
}
